From 19e715b010b98a2976128e72eebbbe178d2e2010 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniele Ceraolo Spurio <daniele.ceraolospurio@intel.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Feb 2023 08:07:42 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 18/22] drm/i915/mtl/huc: auth HuC via GSC

The full authentication via the GSC requires an heci packet submission
to the GSC FW via the GSC CS. The GSC has new PXP command for this
(literally called NEW_HUC_AUTH).
The intel_huc_auth fuction is also updated to handle both authentication
types.

v2: update size calculation for GSC pkt (Alan), rebase on new huc
    printing macros.

Signed-off-by: Daniele Ceraolo Spurio <daniele.ceraolospurio@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Alan Previn <alan.previn.teres.alexis@intel.com>
